763
01:03:42,850 --> 01:03:45,320
<i>[You Are Too Much]</i>

764
01:03:45,320 --> 01:03:48,160
<i>If I tell her to come,
she's ready to run to me.</i>

765
01:03:48,160 --> 01:03:50,930
<i>- She's my woman!
- Because of her</i>

766
01:03:50,930 --> 01:03:55,160
<i>you threw Mom off the cliff?
Go to the police right now.</i>

767
01:03:55,160 --> 01:03:59,450
<i>Was it you who told Hyun Joon what
happened on the day of the incident?</i>

768
01:03:59,450 --> 01:04:01,210
<i>From now on, I'll be watching you.</i>

769
01:04:01,210 --> 01:04:03,190
<i>If you keep doing this,
you're as good as a dead dog.</i>

770
01:04:03,190 --> 01:04:06,070
<i>I'm embarrassed! I'm so embarrassed!</i>

771
01:04:06,070 --> 01:04:08,290
<i>You're embarrassed of both your
mother-in-law and your sister-in-law.</i>

772
01:04:08,290 --> 01:04:11,190
<i>Please persuade him to divorce me.</i>

773
01:04:11,190 --> 01:04:15,030
<i>You won't get involved with
Yoo Ji Na at all, so just sign with me.</i>

774
01:04:15,030 --> 01:04:18,210
<i>- But what if we both end up broke?
- Then, let's run away together!</i>

775
01:04:18,210 --> 01:04:20,030
<i>Yoo Ji Na is not her real name.</i>

776
01:04:20,030 --> 01:04:24,250
<i>Find out everything about
her before her debut.</i>
